data.title: AECOM
data.text:
Along with our client from the Hong Kong Civil Engineering and Development Department, we shared how our innovative use of high strength structural steel in our projects has reduced carbon emissions by up to 22 percent.

“Transitioning out of the military, AECOM gave me the opportunity to put my skills and passion to work through the SkillBridge Program. I’ve always found myself drawn to new challenges and with AECOM I get to take those challenges on with a diverse team of professionals, supported by the amazing veteran community here.”
